curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/7298' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8924", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8924 is a dual operational amplifier designed  for 5V operation. The device can operate from 3V to  5.5V single supply. It provides a wide input common  mode voltage range and rail-to-rail output voltage  swing.  The SGM8924 offers excellent overall performance. It  features low offset, low noise and low distortion.  Meanwhile, low impedance load can be used due to the  characteristics of high output drive capability. The  device works well in low voltage or battery-powered  audio systems requiring high quality.  The SGM8924 is offered in a Green MSOP-10 package.  It is specified over the extended -40 ℃ to +85 ℃  temperature range.      "}'
